ghted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.45633, "shard": "04", "shelf_id": "sn95047246, 1945-09-27, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/fu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["hernando", "brooksville", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida", "newspapers", "hernando county", "hernando county (fla.)"], "subject_headings": ["Brooksville (Fla.)--Newspapers", "Hernando County (Fla.)--Newspapers", "Florida--Hernando County", "United States--Florida--Hernando--Brooksville"], "subjects": [{"brooksville": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:brooksville&fo=json"}, {"brooksville (fla.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:brooksville+%28fla.%29&fo=json"}, {"florida": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:florida&fo=json"}, {"hernando": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hernando&fo=json"}, {"hernando county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hernando+county&fo=json"}, {"hernando county (fla.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hernando+county+%28fla.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2026-01-28T08:59:34.862Z", "title": "The Brooksville journal (Brooksville, Fla.), September 27, 1945", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/1945-09-27/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/"], "batch": ["fu_jennings_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "192?", "description": ["Weekly Ceased in 1959. Also issued on microfilm from the University of Florida. Description based on: Vol. 3, no. 22 (Jan. 2, 1929). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 31, no. 36 (Apr. 9, 1959). Brooksville sun (DLC)sn 98026438 (OCoLC)40537331 Brooksville sun-journal (DLC)sn 95047247 (OCoLC)33425265"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:17.596Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [28.554895, -82.387858], "location": ["hernando", "brooksville", "united states", "florida", "hernando county"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-82.387858, 28.554895], "number": ["sn98026441", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "sn98026438", "sn95047247", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/1928-01-05/ed-1/", "33425264", "1", "2025-05-23t21:30:26", "online resource", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/1959-04-16/ed-1/", "1574", "sn95047246"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the brooksville journal (brooksville, fla.) 1927-1959", "serial and government publications division", "the brooksville journal (brooksville, fla.) 192?-1959"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 87.93188, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn95047246", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd"], "subject": ["hernando", "brooksville", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida", "newspapers", "hernando county", "hernando county (fla.)"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:36:43.276Z", "title": "The Brooksville journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239190/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1927", "dates": ["[1927 TO 1959]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1927. Tampa morning tribune, August 4, 1927, p. 4. Ceased with: Vol. 31, no. 37 (Apr. 16, 1959). Vol. 1, nos. 32-33 repeated by issues for: Mar. 1-8 and 15-22, 1928. Volume numbering erroneously changes from vol. IX, no. 30 (Feb. 27, 1936) to vol. XI, no. 31 (Mar. 5, 1936). Volume number does not change between issues: vol. XIV, no. 52 (Aug. 3, 1939) and vol. XIV, no. 1 (Aug. 10, 1939). Issues for Oct. 12, 19, 26, and Nov. 2, 1939, respectively, called vol. XIV, no. 10, vol. XV, no. 11, vol. XVI, no. 12, and vol. XIII, no. 13. Merged with: Brooksville sun, to form: Brooksville sun-journal. Vol. 1, no. 24 (Jan. 5, 1928); title from banner (loc.gov, viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Vol. 31, no. 37 (Apr. 16, 1959) (viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Brooksville sun Brooksville sun-journal (DLC) 2025239191 (OCoLC)1545792124"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:18.656Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239190/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["hernando", "brooksville", "united states", "florida", "hernando county"], "number": ["1545792193", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2025239189", "2025239191", "2025239190", "online resource"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the brooksville journal (brooksville, fla.) 1927-1959 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 78.615, "shelf_id": "AN2.F6.B78 J6", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["hernando", "brooksville", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida", "newspapers", "hernando county", "hernando county (fla.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:15:09.430Z", "title": "The Brooksville journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2025239190/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239191/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1959", "dates": ["[1959 TO 1963]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with: Vol. 31, no. 38 (Apr. 23, 1959); ceased with: vol. 33, no. 33 (Mar. 7, 1963). Vol. 34, nos. <7>-52 (Sept. <14>, 1961-July 26, 1962) incorrectly called vol. 33, nos. <7>-52; vol. 35, nos. 1-33 (Aug. 2, 1962-Mar. 7, 1963) incorrectly called vol. 33, nos. 1-33. Vol. 31, no. 39 (Apr. 30, 1959); title from banner (loc.gov, viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Vol. 33, no. 33 (Mar. 7, 1963) (viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Sun-journal (Brooksville, Fla. : 1963)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:18.656Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239191/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["hernando", "brooksville", "united states", "florida", "hernando county"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2025239191", "1545792124", "2025239190", "online resource"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Sun-journal"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the brooksville sun-journal (brooksville, fla.) 1959-1963 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 78.615, "shelf_id": "AN2.F6.B78 S86", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["hernando", "brooksville", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida", "newspapers", "hernando county", "hernando county (fla.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:15:09.430Z", "title": "The Brooksville sun-journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2025239191/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/"], "batch": ["fu_lantana_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date":